{"tid":938166,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人類自由指數　港越跌越低","createTime":"2018-12-12T05:44:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T16:38:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"969617a79c09bcbc8ea1e8257558a3d1b3ee84c4","tid":938166,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T05:44:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181212/20566935\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181212%2F20566935&d=O5JMslzyeRwB2U9kY%2FOhh4M9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=8525f499\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181212%2F20566935&h=11fc389d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181212/20566935</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月12日 <br />\n<br />\n人類自由指數　港越跌越低<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181212/large/a0404a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181212%2Flarge%2Fa0404a.gif&h=6b7ff4ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國家主席習近平2013年上任後，香港自由一直衰退。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加拿大智庫弗雷澤研究所前日公佈「2018年人類自由指數」，記錄了2015至16年在「人類自由」的變化。在全球162個國家或地區中，香港總體排名第三，比去年跌一位，整體評分跌0.08分。報告亦花一定篇幅提及香港近年狀況，並表示預料香港評分未來繼續下跌，不感意外。<br />\n<br />\n長達406頁的報告由弗雷澤研究所、美國卡托研究所及德國弗里德里希瑙曼自由基金共同製作並發表，在人類自由的總評分下細分個人自由及經濟自由兩項評分，其中香港經濟自由得第一名，但個人自由僅32名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181212/large/a0404b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181212%2Flarge%2Fa0404b.gif&h=e5f0f309&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n與習上任「很難說是巧合」<br />\n<br />\n報告在前言及摘要均花上一定篇幅提及香港狀況。報告提及銅鑼灣書店事件，指事件違反《基本法》，並以此作例說明中國對人類自由的威脅。報告亦提及數以千計人士在選舉中投票支持有獨立傾向的候選人，此舉引來大陸方面加強介入香港事務，損害自由。<br />\n<br />\n報告又表示香港2014年是全球最自由的司法管轄區，但到2016年排名已跌至第三名，在分數上更自2013年起一直下跌。報告直指香港自由自2013年衰退，與中國國家主席習近平同年上任「很難說成是巧合」。<br />\n<br />\n今年排名前10的國家或地區依次為新西蘭、瑞士、香港、澳洲、加拿大、荷蘭及丹麥並列第六、愛爾蘭及英國並列第八，而台灣、挪威及芬蘭則並列第10。<br />\n<br />\n弗雷澤研究所/中央社  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n內地禁售iPhone「不可上訴」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n西環集中營：建制反美幫倒忙 (季陶)"},{"pid":"89ad438a1d0554b3806ee64a39bfdeca1b2e980e","tid":938166,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:00:02.000Z","msg":"NO U.S.?"},{"pid":"106174e164eef88814d784eb33f73676ced97d52","tid":938166,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:09:08.000Z","msg":"別國又係到說三道四<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8700a3156dd69033ca7b2cc156db5858c44865dd","tid":938166,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:24:10.000Z","msg":"頂你又係加拿大？"},{"pid":"aecfc8206e1025f682ea0ebc76bf0189febdc823","tid":938166,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89ad438a1d0554b3806ee64a39bfdeca1b2e980e","tid":938166,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:00:02.000Z","msg":"NO U.S.?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:24:30.000Z","msg":"世界文明自由領袖美國都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f5e99d602cd9159fa83358634b31d4675d13bb","tid":938166,"uid":38795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T16:35:56.000Z","msg":"香港高過挪威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c678deb422e4614f7eaeca746b1c4a2a255f1483","tid":938166,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T16:36:59.000Z","msg":"港府：不認同XXXXXXX"},{"pid":"134ed2abc2d06dcbc78f5c277614d79c6043fd23","tid":938166,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T16:37:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b40054891aca653871dd9d2